  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC439">
        <l>eñciya mūṉṟu mēlvantu muṭikku</l>
	<l>meñcuporuṭ kiḷavi yilaveṉa moḻipa.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/243/mode/1up">243</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/244/mode/1up">244</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, oḻintu niṉṟa eccaṅkaṭiṟattup paṭuvatōr ilakkaṇam uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : eñciya mūṉṟum eṉpaṉa, avai mūṉṟum ; muntaiyavaṟṟaippōlat tammai yiṉṉavantu muṭippaṉa eṉṟu kāṭṭappaṭum eccaccol illai eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>mūṉṟum mēlvantu muṭikkum eccaccol ila eṉa, oṉṟu uṭaitteṉpatām. aḵtiyātōveṉiṉ colleccam; ataṉai muṉṉarc collutum.	(43)</p>
   </body>
  </text>

